Use the standard library
This is how to Strongest_Extension of class_name and extensions:
  Remember that best_extension is item 0 in extensions
  Remember that best_strength is 0
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this extensions's length times:
    Remember that current_extension is item i in extensions
    Remember that upper_count is 0
    Remember that lower_count is 0
    Remember that j is 0
    Do this current_extension's length times:
      Remember that ch is item j in current_extension
      When ch is in "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ", then:
        Increase upper_count
      But, if not:
        When ch is in "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz", then:
          Increase lower_count
        End when
      End when
      Increase j
    End do
    Remember that strength is diff of upper_count and lower_count
    When strength is more than best_strength, then:
      Remember that best_strength is strength
      Remember that best_extension is current_extension
    End when
    Increase i
  End do
  The answer is sum of class_name and "." and best_extension
Now you know